---
import meImage from "../../assets/me.png";

const { class: className = "" } = Astro.props;
---

<article
  class:list={[
    "profile-card flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col justify-start gap-8 overflow-hidden rounded-4xl bg-white p-6 sm:aspect-[465/228] lg:aspect-auto",
    className,
  ]}
  aria-labelledby="profile-title"
>
  <img
    src={meImage.src}
    width={meImage.width}
    height={meImage.height}
    alt="Shuntarouの顔アイコン"
    class="size-16 object-contain sm:size-18"
  />

  <div class="min-w-0 space-y-2">
    <h1 id="profile-title" class="min-w-0 leading-tight text-black lg:whitespace-nowrap">
      <span class="text-base font-normal">I'm</span>
      <span class="ml-2 font-serif-display text-2xl font-bold">
        Shuntarou.
      </span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium">
        a developer and designer from Tokushima.
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="line-clamp-2 max-w-xl text-xs font-medium leading-relaxed text-black/40 sm:hidden lg:block">
      こんにちわ、IT学科1年次の秦駿太朗です。出身は徳島で、趣味はゴルフ、Podcast、ゲーム(MOBA)などです。よろしくお願いします。
    </p>
  </div>
</article>
